wikipedia_page.main: David Paintin Hon FFSRH MB ChB FRCOG (18 December 1930 – 30 March 2019)  was a British doctor and an emeritus reader in obstetrics and gynaecology at the University of London. He was a former chair of the Birth Control Trust and worked on the campaign to pass the 1967 Abortion Act. David Paintin died on 30 March 2019.
